OL,6,FJustin Welby is facing a growing
OL,7,Fbacklash over his failure to tackle
OL,8,Fknown child abuse within the Church of
OL,9,FEngland
OL,11,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury is facing
OL,12,Fmounting pressure to resign over his
OL,13,Fhandling of child abuse allegations
OL,14,Fagainst a barrister and former member
OL,15,Fof the Church of England.
