OL,3,CPressure mounts on Archbishop of
OL,4,CCanterbury to resign over abuse case
OL,6,FA petition by some members of the
OL,7,FGeneral Synod ` the church's
OL,8,Fparliament ` has gathered more than
OL,9,F10,000 signatures urging Justin Welby
OL,10,Fto stand down over his "failures" to
OL,11,Falert authorities about John Smyth
OL,12,FQC's "abhorrent" abuse of children and
OL,13,Fyoung men.
OL,15,FA recent review described Smyth, who
OL,16,Fdied in 2018, as the most prolific
OL,17,Fabuser associated with the Church of
OL,18,FEngland.
