OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer said the victims of
OL,7,FSmyth were "failed very, very badly",
OL,8,Fbut would not comment directly on
OL,9,Fwhether the Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,10,Fshould quit.
OL,12,FThe prime minister said: "Let me be
OL,13,Fclear: of what I know of the
OL,14,Fallegations, they are clearly horrific
OL,15,Fin relation to this particular case,
OL,16,Fboth in their scale and their content.
OL,18,F"My thoughts, as they are in all of
OL,19,Fthese issues, are with the victims
OL,20,Fhere who have obviously been failed
OL,21,Fvery, very badly.
