OL,6,F"It's a matter, in the end, for the
OL,7,Fchurch, but I'm not going to shy away
OL,8,Ffrom the fact of saying that these are
OL,9,Fhorrific allegations and that my
OL,10,Fthoughts are with the victims in
OL,11,Frelation to it."
OL,13,FOne of Smyth's victims, Andrew Morse,
OL,14,Fhas joined calls for the Archbishop to
OL,15,Fresign.
OL,17,FMr Morse told BBC Radio 4 he was
OL,18,Fabused by Smyth while he was a pupil
OL,19,Fat Winchester College, including
OL,20,Frepeated beating which later led to
OL,21,Fhis attempt suicide.
