OL,6,FMr Morse said: "I think he should
OL,7,Fresign; I think the church is
OL,8,Fincredibly stringent with its rules
OL,9,Ffor everyday vicars and those lower
OL,10,Fdown the scale about what to do when
OL,11,Fabuse is reported to you.
OL,13,F"The Archbishop has himself admitted
OL,14,Fthat he failed in 2013 and I think for
OL,15,Fthat reason, although on a personal
OL,16,Flevel I know how difficult it is not
OL,17,Fto hold on to secrets and particularly
OL,18,Fsecrets in which you yourself come out
OL,19,Fmaybe with a degree of shame, I
OL,20,Fbelieve that now is an opportunity for
OL,21,Fhim to resign."
