OL,6,FHe added that it would be an
OL,7,F"opportunity" for Mr Welby to "stand
OL,8,Fwith the victims of Smyth's abuse" if
OL,9,Fhe were to resign.
OL,11,FThe Makin review, published last week,
OL,12,Ffound that Mr Welby was presented with
OL,13,Fthe evidence in 2013, and concluded
OL,14,Fthat Smyth could've been brought to
OL,15,Fjustice a decade earlier had the
OL,16,FArchbishop of Canterbury reported it
OL,17,Fto the police.
