OL,6,FThe report said Smyth "could and
OL,7,Fshould have been formally reported to
OL,8,Fthe police in the UK, and to
OL,9,Fauthorities in South Africa (church
OL,10,Fauthorities and potentially the
OL,11,Fpolice) by church officers, including
OL,12,Fa diocesan bishop and Justin Welby in
OL,13,F2013.
OL,15,FSmyth ran Christian summer camps in
OL,16,Fthe 1970s and 1980s and is said to
OL,17,Fhave physically and sexually abused
OL,18,F130 boys and young men in the UK and
OL,19,FSouth Africa over five decades until
OL,20,Fhis death in 2018.
