OL,6,FThe review said Smyth was "never
OL,7,Fbrought to justice for the abuse"
OL,8,Fafter he died aged 75 in Cape Town
OL,9,Fwhile under investigation by Hampshire
OL,10,FPolice.
OL,12,FMr Welby previously said he had "no
OL,13,Fidea or suspicion of this abuse"
OL,14,Fbefore 2013 but knew Smyth because of
OL,15,Fhis attendance at Iwerne Christian
OL,16,Fcamps in the 1970s.
OL,18,FThe review said there was no evidence
OL,19,Fthat he had "maintained any
OL,20,Fsignificant contact" with the
OL,21,Fbarrister in later years.
