OL,6,FThe Archbishop has since apologised
OL,7,Fafter the review was published and
OL,8,Facknowledged he had "personally failed
OL,9,Fto ensure" it was "energetically
OL,10,Finvestigated".
OL,12,FHowever, he has maintained he will not
OL,13,Fresign, with a Lambeth Palace
OL,14,Fspokesperson saying the Archbishop
OL,15,F"hopes the Makin Review supports the
OL,16,Fongoing work of building a safer
OL,17,Fchurch here and around the world".
OL,19,FITV News understands that Mr Welby has
OL,20,Fcleared his calendar of all
OL,21,Fengagements on Tuesday.
