OL,6,FMeanwhile, Nick Timothy MP requested
OL,7,Fan urgent question on the matter of
OL,8,FArchbishop Welby's future in the House
OL,9,Fof Commons, which was declined.
OL,11,FThe Dean of Chapel at King's College
OL,12,FCambridge has added to calls for the
OL,13,FArchbishop of Canterbury to resign.
OL,15,FDr Stephen Cherry, former canon of
OL,16,FDurham Cathedral, told BBC Radio 4's
OL,17,FToday programme: "I think he really
OL,18,Fneeds to now tender his resignation
OL,19,Fand allow there to be significant
OL,20,Fchange.
