OL,6,FThe Bishop of Newcastle, Helen-Ann
OL,7,FHartley, told the BBC the church is
OL,8,F"in danger of losing complete
OL,9,Fcredibility" in safeguarding.
OL,11,FOf Mr Welby, she said: "I think,
OL,12,Fsadly, his position is untenable, so I
OL,13,Fthink he should resign."
OL,15,FAnother survivor of Smyth's abuse
OL,16,Fdemanded a "clean sweep" of senior
