OL,3,CPressure mounts on Archbishop of
OL,4,CCanterbury to resign over abuse case
OL,6,FMark Stibbe told the BBC on Monday
OL,7,Fthat the positions of senior members
OL,8,Fof the church involved in a cover-up
OL,9,Fare all untenable.
OL,11,FHe said: "I would also apply that to
OL,12,Fthe bishops that knew and did nothing,
OL,13,Fand the senior clergy of the Church of
OL,14,FEngland that knew and did nothing.
OL,16,F"Their positions are also untenable."
OL,18,FOn Tuesday, the Energy Security
OL,19,FSecretary, Ed Miliband said the abuse
OL,20,Fby Smyth was "horrifying" but didn't
OL,21,Fjoin calls for Mr Welby to resign.
