OL,6,FHe told ITV's Good Morning Britain:
OL,7,F"I'm not going to second-guess
OL,8,Fdecisions that are the Church of
OL,9,FEngland's decisions and decisions for
OL,10,FJustin Welby.
OL,12,F"Obviously, the catalogue of abuse
OL,13,Fthat has been uncovered is deeply,
OL,14,Fdeeply disturbing, but the Church of
OL,15,FEngland makes its own decisions on
OL,16,Fthese matters, and I think it's right
OL,17,Fthat I, as a politician, don't
OL,18,Fintervene in those."
